text: Black Girl (original French title: La noire de...) is a 1966 French Senegalese drama movie directed by Ousmane Sembène and starring Mbissine Thérèse Diop, Anne-Marie Jelinek, Robert Fontaine, Momar Nar Sene. == Other websites == * Category:1966 drama movies Category:French drama movies Category:Senegalese movies Category:Movies directed by Ousmane Sembène
